02:25:00,838 --> 02:25:02,780
Point of information of Vice President Marks.

1449
02:25:03,340 --> 02:25:06,483
The councilor mentioned that he asked for the assessment back several months.

1450
02:25:06,543 --> 02:25:08,204
Did we get a copy of the assessment?

1451
02:25:08,845 --> 02:25:09,765
I believe we got it.

1452
02:25:11,046 --> 02:25:12,367
We were supposed to get it on the 31st.

1453
02:25:12,407 --> 02:25:13,969
We haven't got it yet according to the meeting.

